010/extras/c285a8158e69154eb3a953b7a4b63134.webm?t=1663956348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013010/extras/c285a8158e69154eb3a953b7a4b63134.mp4?t=1663956348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 使用掷骰子防止触发敌人技能。每一回合敌人都会掷公司骰子来触发技能，你需要为它做风险管理。把骰子放在你想要阻止的技能上，它会让你减少可用的骰子。承受风险还是避开风险, 是你的决定。<br><br></li><li> 当公司筹集到特定的金额时，新的董事会成员将继续加入。那个时候，你什么也做不了，只能看着公司越来越强大。确保在为时已晚之前建立自己的优势吧。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"[imgvid poster.avif=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013010/extras/2b66b21b8a3f3122480c99ab8876505b.poster.avif?t=1663956348\" mp4=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013010/extras/2b66b21b8a3f3122480c99ab8876505b.mp4?t=1663956348\" webm=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013010/extras/2b66b21b8a3f3122480c99ab8876505b.webm?t=1663956348\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\"]\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" /></span>[/imgvid]\n\n[*] 当您获得足够的资源时，您需要冒险打开一张未知的证据卡。如果你有足够的线索资源，你可以将它们兑换成你的胜利点数！否则，证据卡会触发事件，后果自负。\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" mp4=\"\" webm=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\"][/imgvid]\n\n[*] 小心你的压力水平，当它达到 10 时，它会让你崩溃！\n[imgvid poster.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013010/extras/2b66b21b8a3f3122480c99ab8876505b.poster.avif?t=1663956348\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013010/extras/2b66b21b8a3f3122480c99ab8876505b.webm?t=1663956348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2013010/extras/2b66b21b8a3f3122480c99ab8876505b.mp4?t=1663956348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> 当您获得足够的资源时，您需要冒险打开一张未知的证据卡。如果你有足够的线索资源，你可以将它们兑换成你的胜利点数！否则，证据卡会触发事件，后果自负。<br><span class=\"bb_im